&lt;pre&gt;Discussed at today's API OWNERs. LGTM1 on the condition that we make sure 
there's a flag for rollout so that this can be kill-switched if the compat 
issues turn out to be problematic for other sites.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

