&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20250410" rel="nofollow"&gt;Thu, 10 Apr 2025 18:28:53 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
