&gt;&gt; Regarding potential open spec issues, I found 6
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues?q=is%3Aopen+label%3Acss-values-5+attr+in%3Atitle"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues?q=is%3Aopen+label%3Acss-values-5+attr+in%3Atitle&lt;/a&gt;&gt;,
