Specification &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-4/#predefined"&gt;https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-4/#predefined&lt;/a&gt;

Summary

&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Display P3, Rec2020, ProPhoto RGB and a98 RGB are specified in CSS 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;color 4 as predefined color spaces but had not yet been implemented as 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;color spaces for interpolation. Other UAs have already implemented.
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Blink component Blink&gt;CSS 
&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3ECSS%22"&gt;https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3ECSS%22&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
