&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3ctag/design-reviews/issues/1001#issuecomment-2750966335"&gt;https://github.com/w3ctag/design-reviews/issues/1001#issuecomment-2750966335&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; .
